---
title: Gochujang Salmon Poke Bowl with Sesame Sweet Potato and Smacked Cucumber
description: Poke, pronounced poh-kay, is one of Hawaii's most well-known dishes. Poke means 'to slice' or 'cut crosswise into pieces', so we've made a delicious Korean inspired version for our Gochujang Salmon Poke Bowl.
